  FontSize->0.9 Inherited,ExpressionUUID->
  "5fdd79ad-6088-4170-b02c-2bc77905614d"],
 ". The state vector confirms it:"
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"fda9957a-1538-4549-ba5b-4c10b74ebe98"],

