  FontSize->0.9 Inherited,ExpressionUUID->
  "eb87d027-0450-4303-bdc5-5cf6d0898ac1"],
 ", and here a sign appears for the first time: ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  TemplateBox[{"1"},
   "Ket"]], "InlineFormula",
  FontSize->0.9 Inherited,ExpressionUUID->
  "e90e23b0-b0b8-405c-80b4-86604a44f12d"],
 " is the ",
 Cell[BoxData[
