Cell["\<\
Time the entropy of this thousand-qubit GHZ state to see that it is \
essentially instantaneous:\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"7953143f-0e41-4191-b1b6-684238c980bc"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"AbsoluteTiming", "[", 
